description: This common Chukcha purrs with a rating of 52, and a multiplier of 2x. It has a total score of 104, and confers the same amount of votes in the EtherCats DAO. The card game properties are 8 for North, Leverage for East, Box for South, and Box for West. Chukcha has the personality suit of quant. Each Founders Series cat is part of NFT history. These fine felines represent the first verifiably random packs minted with Chainlink VRF.
name: Chukcha [104 Votes, Common]
